headline: 5 Stocks to Add to Your Portfolio From the Prospering P&C Insurance Industry
summary: Zacks Property and Casualty Insurance players like TRV, ALL, CINF, CNA and AXS are likely to benefit from digitization and catastrophes that drive policy renewal rate and pricing.
